This is the README file for Lingua::ZH::Wrap, a simple Chinese text
wrapper.

* Installation

Lingua::ZH::Wrap uses the standard perl module install process:

cpansign -v		# see SIGNATURE for details
perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install

